{%- comment -%}
Snippet: Article Tag
Description: This snippet is used to display a tag for an article.

Accepts:
- blog_handle: The handle of the blog the article is in.
- article_tag: The tag to display.

Usage:
{% render 'article-tag', blog_handle:'news', article_tag:'beauty' %}
{%- endcomment -%}

<div class='article-tag border border-gray py-[5px] px-[23px] hover:border-black hover:text-white2 hover:bg-black transition-all'>
  <a
    href='/blogs/{{ blog_handle }}/tagged/{{ article_tag | handleize }}'
    aria-label="{{ 'general.check_out' | t }} {{ article_tag | escape }}"
    class='article-tag__name text-center text-14 uppercase'>
    {{ article_tag }}
  </a>
</div>
